# Vitality Base runs with NO environment variables. Fork, deploy, done.
#
# OPTIONAL: turn on real cross-device saving with your own free Supabase project.
# Leave these blank to stay on local (per-device) saving.
#
# 1. Create a free project at https://supabase.com
# 2. Run supabase/tile_data.sql in its SQL editor
# 3. Fill these in (Project Settings -> API), here and in your Vercel env:
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
